Name: 愤怒的小鸟太空版
Author: sgb76 <sgb76@163.com>
More:
Angry Birds Space Edition is a casual puzzle game developed by Rovio Entertainment based on the previous game "Angry Birds". In the game, players need to use slingshots to launch various birds on other planets to attack buildings and pigs, and eliminate all pigs in the level.

Unlock Key:CGFU-ECYT-QPCN-MZYA

Register and play any paid level to successfully unlock the game.
